#80001
A Rich, Velvet-walled Hallway~
Upon crossing the threshold, it is immediately apparant that those who

make it into the inner sanctum of this guild subscribe to the belief

'Enjoy life while it is yours to enjoy'.  The walls are lined with soft,

blood-red velvet, making the hall at once beautiful, and quiet as a tomb. 

On both sides of the hall, there is a portait of exquisite quality,

showing that in this society, crime does indeed pay quite well.

