A Passage Lined with Statues~
Lining the walls in this portion of the hallway are detailed busts,

perhaps of former guild leaders, lined up on a polished basalt table

along the left side.  The statues are of different stones: a jade goblin,

a marble vyan, and an alabastar human.  Their jeweled eyes twinkle

avaraciously in the dim candlelight as you pass.

